        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Rural Physician Workforce Production Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill allows hospitals and critical access hospitals to receive payment under Medicare for each resident that receives training in a rural training location, in accordance with specified criteria and limitations.</p>]]></text>
